                            <comment id="15472174" author="shivaram" created="Wed, 7 Sep 2016 23:52:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I think we missed passing the options through when we converted to the new writer API in &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/spark/commit/cc4d5229c98a589da76a4d5e5fdc5ea92385183b&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/spark/commit/cc4d5229c98a589da76a4d5e5fdc5ea92385183b&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The fix is probably just to add a line `write &amp;lt;- callJMethod(write, &quot;options&quot;, options)` &amp;#8211; Feel free to send a PR if you get a chance or I&apos;ll send one later tonight&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;cc &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=felixcheung&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;felixcheung&quot;&gt;felixcheung&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
